title: Spot-breasted thornbird
text: The spot-breasted thornbird ("Phacellodomus maculipectus") is a species of <a href="bird">bird</a> in the family <a href="Furnariidae">Furnariidae</a>. It is found in the <a href="Southern%20Andean%20Yungas">Southern Andean Yungas</a>. Its natural <a href="habitat">habitat</a>s are subtropical or tropical dry <a href="forest">forest</a>s and subtropical or tropical high-altitude <a href="shrubland">shrubland</a>.
